<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Share Your Experience</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
  <table width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0;">{{hotelName}}</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 10px 0 0 0;">How was your stay?</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
              <h2 style="color: #333333; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Dear {{guestName}},</h2>
              <p style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                Thank you for staying with us! We would love to hear about your experience.
                Your feedback helps us improve our services and assist future guests.
              </p>
              <p style="color: #888; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Booking #{{bookingId}} | Checkout: {{checkOutDate}}</p>
              <a href="{{reviewLink}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0;">
                Leave a Review
              </a>
              <p style="color: #999; font-size: 13px; margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                It only takes a minute and means a lot to us.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px;">© {{currentYear}} {{hotelName}}</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
